description.en: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.ar: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.br: Um fogo de artifício projetado especificamente para iniciantes. Não irá incomodar seus vizinhos, a menos que o telhado deles pegue fogo!
description.cns: 为新手特制的烟花。放心，不会吵到你的邻居，除非他们屋顶着火！
description.fi: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.fil: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.fr: Catégorie 1 : artifices de divertissement qui présentent un danger très faible et un niveau sonore négligeable et qui sont destinés à être utilisés dans des espaces confinés, y compris les artifices de divertissement destinés à être utilisés à l'intérieur d'immeubles d'habitation.
description.id: Kembang api yang dirancang khusus untuk pemula. Tidak akan mengganggu tetanggamu kecuali atap mereka terbakar!
description.it: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.jp: 初心者のための花火です。屋根にさえ引火させなければ、近所迷惑にはならないってｗ
description.kr: 초보자를 위해 특별히 고안된 불꽃 놀이. 지붕에 불이 붙지 않으면 이웃을 괴롭히지 않을 것입니다!
description.nl: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.pl: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.ru: Фейрверк, специально разработанный для новичков. Не будет мешать вашим соседям до момента, пока у них не загорится крыша!
description.sp: Fuegos artificiales diseñados específicamente para principiantes. ¡No molestarás a tus vecinos a menos que el techo se incendie!
description.sw: A firework specifically designed for beginners. Won't annoy your neighbours unless their roof catches fire!
description.th: ดอกไม้ไฟที่ออกแบบมาสำหรับผู้เริ่มต้นโดยเฉพาะ จะไม่รบกวนเพื่อนบ้านของคุณเว้นแต่หลังคาของพวกเขาจะถูกไฟไหม้!
description.tw: 專為初學者設計的煙火，不會讓你的鄰居氣到中風，除非燒到他家屋頂。
description.vi: Pháo hoa được thiết kế đặc biệt cho người mới bắt đầu. Sẽ không làm phiền hàng xóm của bạn trừ khi mái nhà của họ bắt lửa!
